title: Healthy Hair Begins Inside Your Dryer!
description: Learn why an FHI Brands professional dryer is the best choice for healthy, shiny hair!

asset.author: FHIHeat
asset.description: Learn why an FHI Brands professional dryer is the best choice for healthy, shiny hair!

transcripts: Healthy hair begins inside the tool where professional grade materials like tourmaline ceramic infuse negative ions into the hair producing high caliber high shine results when compared to inexpensive bargain dryers. The FHI brands dryer is a powerhouse as the air is pulled through the high-efficiency motor the coils and tourmaline ceramic mix with the air steadily warming and charging it with negative ions that condition and protect the hair traditional heat overpowers and boils the moisture out of the hair leaving tried damage to vehicles the tourmaline ceramic heat of an shi brands dryer breaks down water molecules into smaller particles to penetrate allowing the hair to maintain essential moisture.
